        "lang": "en",
        "text": "So he took his men, divided them into three companies and set an ambush in the fields. When he saw the people coming out of the city, he rose to attack them."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "he divided his men into three groups and set an ambush in the fields. When Abimelech saw the people coming out of the city, he and his men jumped up from their hiding places and attacked them."
      }
